Compile i686 crosscompiler:
sudo ./build.sh i686/build-crosstools-i686.sh

Clean working directory:
sudo ./build.sh i686/build-crosstools-i686.sh clean

Compile mini system:
./build.sh i686/build-linux-basic.sh clean
./build.sh i686/build-linux-basic.sh

Compile full distro:
./build.sh i686/build-linux.sh clean
./build.sh i686/build-linux.sh
